<li id="cite_note-60"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-60">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/ics/journal/papers/issue45/p097-140.pdf">"明太祖《紀非錄》書後：秦周齊潭魯代靖江諸王罪行敘錄"</a> (PDF)<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/ics/journal/papers/issue45/p097-140.pdf">http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/ics/journal/papers/issue45/p097-140.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 13 November 2011</span>.</span></span></li>
